# Personal Finance Tracker - Mendix App

A complete personal finance management application built with Mendix low-code platform.

## Features
- ✅ Account management (Checking, Savings, Credit Card)
- ✅ Category management (Income/Expense categories)
- ✅ Transaction tracking with account and category relationships
- ✅ Responsive web interface
- ✅ CRUD operations for all entities
- ✅ Professional data grids and forms

## Tech Stack
- **Platform**: Mendix 11.2.0
- **Database**: Built-in Mendix database
- **UI Framework**: Atlas UI (Mendix)
- **Deployment**: Mendix Cloud

## Project Structure
- **Entities**: Account, Category, Transaction
- **Pages**: Overview and NewEdit pages for each entity
- **Navigation**: Menu-driven interface
- **Associations**: Transaction → Account, Transaction → Category

## How to Run
1. Download the .mpk file from `/project-package/`
2. Import into Mendix Studio Pro
3. Run locally or deploy to Mendix Cloud

